snippet.title: Gem Setter - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY THE GAME: https://onefin.itch.io/gem-setter

gem setter is a block sliding puzzle game with a level editor. think through over 50 built-in levels, then build your own creations and share them with the world!

SOUNDTRACK PREMIERE: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bjm4KrFe5Dk
